/// 1. token transfer (1 input, 0 output):          F (once per tree)
/// 2. token transfer (0 input, 1 output):          F (once per tree)
/// 3. token transfer (1 input, 1 output):          F (once per tree)
/// 4. transfer with 2 inputs, 1 address:           F + 1*A
///    Transfers rollover and network fees.

